text: Mühlehorn was a municipality of the canton of Glarus in Switzerland. On 1 January 2011, the former municpalities of Mühlehorn, Bilten, Filzbach, Mollis, Näfels, Niederurnen, Oberurnen and Obstalden merged into the new municipality of Glarus Nord. ==Other websites== *Official website of Mühlehorn Category:Former municipalities of Glarus Category:2011 disestablishments in Switzerland
